OL,5, The Swiss government is discriminating 
OL,6, against men in its rules on pension    
OL,7, benefits, the European Court of Human  
OL,8, Rights (ECHR) has found.               
OL,10,FThe decision will cost millions in     
OL,11,Fbackdated payments, and force the      
OL,12,Fgovernment to rewrite pension law.     
OL,14,FCurrently, women whose husbands die are
OL,15,Fpaid a pension for the rest of their   
OL,16,Flives, while men only receive payments 
OL,17,Fif they have children under 18.        
OL,19,FThe "male breadwinner" concept is not  
OL,20,Fenough to justify this, the ECHR found.
